| Approach                     | Latency    | Legal / ToS risk | Cost       | Difficulty  |
| ---------------------------- | ---------- | ---------------- | ---------- | ----------- |
| TheOddsAPI / SportsData.io   | 1–5 s      | ✅ Safe           | Low–medium | Easy        |
| Genius / LSports feed        | 100–500 ms | ✅ Safe           | High       | Medium      |
| Headless scraper             | 5–15 s     | ⚠️ Risky         | Low        | Medium–hard |
| Custom reverse-engineered WS | < 1 s      | ❌ ToS-breaking   | Free       | Hard        |
